    "cost_rationale": "Three subtasks with minimum necessary decomposition: (1) SAM licensing query (mid-tier: multi-table join on SKU/license tables), (2) consumption spend query (mid-tier: aggregation across fact tables by user and product), (3) reconciliation with classification (frontier-tier: cross-source signal reconciliation, variance analysis with variance explanation, over/under-provisioning posture classification, and cost impact quantification). The cross_recon subtask handles all downstream analysis including classification and recommendation generation in a single frontier call to handle the complexity of multi-signal comparison and contextual posture assignment."
